OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,FAnn Widdecombe, a former Tory Home
OL,7,FOffice minister who later became a
OL,8,FBrexit Party MEP under Nigel Farage,
OL,9,Fhas died aged 78.
OL,11,FWiddecombe retired as an MP in 2010,
OL,12,Fhaving served the constituency of
OL,13,FMaidstone and The Weald since 1987.
OL,15,FA statement from her management said:
OL,16,F"It is with great sadness that today
OL,17,Fwe announce the death of the Rt Hon
OL,18,FAnn Widdecombe, DSG.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
