OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,F"We send our deepest condolences to
OL,7,FAnn's family and friends. We ask that
OL,8,Fthe family's wish not to be contacted
OL,9,Fat this sad time is respected."
OL,11,FAfter her retirement, Widdecombe
OL,12,Fbecame a TV personality and appeared
OL,13,Fon Strictly Come Dancing the same
OL,14,Fyear, where she was partnered by Anton
OL,15,Fdu Beke, winning the support of some
OL,16,Fviewers despite receiving low marks
OL,17,Ffrom the judges.
OL,19,FShe was a runner-up in Big Brother in
OL,20,F2018.
