OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,FThe former Tory shadow home secretary
OL,7,Fwas a committed Brexiter. She sat in
OL,8,Fthe European Parliament until 2020
OL,9,Fafter winning the South West England
OL,10,Fseat for the Brexit Party.
OL,12,FBorn in Bath, Widdecombe was known for
OL,13,Fholding traditional values and
OL,14,Fconservatism. A committed Christian,
OL,15,Fshe opposed granting LGBT people legal
OL,16,Frights such as the same age of consent
OL,17,Fas heterosexuals, and opposed the
OL,18,Frepeal of Section 28. She was anti-
OL,19,Fabortion and an opponent of assisted
OL,20,Fdying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
