OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe famously clashed with her
OL,12,FConservative colleague Michael Howard,
OL,13,Fwhen she was a Home Office minister
OL,14,Fand he was the Home Secretary,
OL,15,Fdescribing him as having "something of
OL,16,Fthe night about him".
OL,18,FWiddecombe also faced flak for
OL,19,Fdefending a policy of chaining
OL,20,Fpregnant prisoners to their beds.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@TO]
