OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,FIn 2023, Widdecombe joined Nigel
OL,7,FFarage's Reform UK, the successor to
OL,8,Fthe Brexit Party, and, the following
OL,9,Fyear, appeared at its party conference
OL,10,Fas Reform's immigration spokesperson.
OL,12,FIn a statement, her management team,
OL,13,FCloud9 Management, said the former MP
OL,14,F"loved the cut and thrust of political
OL,15,Fdebate" and was a "consummate
OL,16,Fprofessional".
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@GO]wD@SOUxD@MO]
