PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783756130
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,F"Never afraid to send herself up, Ann
OL,7,Floved her musical tribute by Victoria
OL,8,FWood and was always game for a laugh,
OL,9,Fhappy to play up to her public persona
OL,10,Fas a grumpy old woman or the panto
OL,11,Fvillain," it said.
OL,13,F"For many, of course, she will be best
OL,14,F(or worst?) remembered for her
OL,15,Funforgettable appearances on Strictly
OL,16,FCome Dancing, defying the judges week-
OL,17,Fafter-week as the public delighted in
OL,18,Fher unsuccessful attempts to follow
OL,19,Fthe choreography of the long-suffering
OL,20,FAnton Du Beke."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
