OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe, former Conservative
OL,4,Cand Brexit Party MP, has died aged 78
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "A consummate
OL,7,Fprofessional and a delight to work
OL,8,Fwith, indefatigable to the last, we
OL,9,Fknow this news will come as a great
OL,10,Fshock to the many colleagues and
OL,11,Ffriends she made along the way and our
OL,12,Fsympathies go to them and her family."
